Album: ALL-AMERIKKKAN BADA$$Artiste: Joey Bada$$Genre: Hip hop, rapRelease: April 7, 2017Joey&rsquo;s Sophomore album contains deep lyricism, which touches on the current political situation in America. He also delves into issues of racism and recognises his personal triumph as a rapper. The album features guest appearances from ScHoolboy Q, Kirk Knight, Styles P, and J Cole. Essential tracks on the 12-track project include &ldquo;For My People,&rdquo; &ldquo;Land of the Free,&rdquo; &ldquo;Devastated,&rdquo; &ldquo;Rockabye Baby,&rdquo; &ldquo;Babylon&rdquo; and &ldquo;Legendary&rdquo;. Joey&rsquo;s project is one of the years biggest hip hop albums. He solidifies his place as one of the best rappers of our generation.Star Rating:4 out of 5